  "title": "Better Than Llamas",
  "description": "What could be better except some real fancy dapper llamas?",
  "body": "<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/tDYBzXM0/images/627ffb9b9ee5ab708b70693f0cd030767e990012.png\" alt=\"A cream colored llama with a green bow tie, curly moustache, pipe, monocle and a top hat with a green band\" width=\"965\" height=\"516\" />\n<br/>\nThe proud successor to <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-than-bunnies\">Better Than Bunnies</a> is here! Dapper Llamas is here to<br/>make your world fancy!\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/tDYBzXM0/images/32271313c58ecdeca7e0ac1741254c34dd78d454.png\" alt=\"A cream colored llama with a green bow tie and top hat. A child llama is following closely behind it with a bow tie, pipe, curly moustache and a fez on the top of its head\" width=\"965\" height=\"516\" />\n<br/>\nFezs and curly moustaches totally included.\n</center>\n<br/>\nParts of model by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RazzleberryFox\">RazzleberryFox</a>.\n<br/>\n<br/>Individual parts of the outfit can be disabled, and llamas are randomly weighted for fanciness, allowing for many, many different variations!\n<br/>\n<br/>\nMod is client-side only.\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Wyld/status/846489501320982528\">#BlameWyld</a>",
